fields.name: patient
fields.description: Patient unique identifier

fields.name: study
fields.description: Imaging study unique indentifier. These are ordered chronologically

fields.name: image
fields.description: A unique identifier for an image within a study. Images are numbered with priority given to frontal view positions, then lateral, then other.

fields.name: view
fields.description: The plane the images was taken of. {0: frontal, 1: lateral, 2: other}

fields.name: dataset
fields.description: The dataset the image is part of. {0: train, 1: validation}

fields.name: path
fields.description: The relative path to the .jpg file.

fields.name: no_finding
fields.description: A label generated by named entity extraction on the radiology note. {0: not mentioned, 1: negative, 2: uncertain, 3: positive}
